                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860830-20-off107 t17860830-20-cd108"></join> last, a cotton gown, value 15 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17860830-20-victim295" type="victimName">
                     Sarah Isabella 
                     Armstrong
                  <interp inst="t17860830-20-victim295" type="surname" value="Armstrong"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17860830-20-victim295" type="given" value="Sarah Isabella"></interp>
